REM Plug in to the Visual Studio.NET 2003 help system
InnovaHxReg /R /P /productnamespace:MS.VSCC.2003 /producthxt:_DEFAULT /namespace:Spring.NET /hxt:_DEFAULT

REM This FilterQuery is minimal.
